  "system": {
    "biography": "<p>A thrall (no accepted taxonomy) made when a vampire or nosferatu drains a victim's Essence to 0 and feeds it their blood. It keeps its former self's attributes and serves its master.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Immunity to Age, Immunity to Normal Weapons</p><p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Dietary Requirement (Essence from its vampire/nosferatu master), Essence Loss</p><p><em>Attacks: Humanoid. Habitat: With its vampiric/nosferatu master. Range: Throughout Europe. Attributes are the original character's, with minimums Strength 4 and Willpower 5; current Essence = 1D6 (minimum 2), suppliable by the master. Set its attributes to match the host. Gains 1 Essence per box of harm it makes a victim do under its master's influence; loses 1 Essence erratically (1D6 months). PAE p.105.</em></p>",
